      <title>尽管美国柴油进口量激增，但欧洲柴油进口量仍将下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/european-diesel-imports-set-to-fall-despite-surging-us-flows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管来自美国的柴油进口量激增，但由于其他主要供应国的进口量减少，欧洲 12 月份的柴油进口量仍将降至数月来的最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/european-diesel-imports-set-to-fall-despite-surging-us-flows</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 16:45:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Shutterfly 首席执行官谈消费者趋势和人工智能</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-17/shutterfly-ceo-on-consumer-trends-ai-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Shutterfly 首席执行官 Sally Pofcher 表示，他们将在这个假日季制作超过 2 亿张贺卡，并预计新年贺卡和相册的数量将有所增长。她在“The Close”节目中与 Scarlet Fu 和 Romaine Bostick 进行了交谈。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-17/shutterfly-ceo-on-consumer-trends-ai-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 16:35:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Intrum 放弃与反对票据持有人的协议，继续执行第 11 章破产保护</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/intrum-scraps-holdout-noteholder-deal-to-proceed-with-chapter-11</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞典 Intrum AB 表示，其与少数票据持有人达成的债务重组纠纷解决协议未能赢得数月前支持该提议的债权人的支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/intrum-scraps-holdout-noteholder-deal-to-proceed-with-chapter-11</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 16:31:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲为何无法摆脱对俄罗斯能源的依赖</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/why-europe-can-t-give-up-russian-gas-despite-sanctions-over-ukraine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[三年前，俄罗斯是世界上最大的天然气出口国，欧洲是其最大的客户。对于欧洲大陆的领导人来说，能够享用俄罗斯的廉价能源比与普京总统做生意的顾虑更重要。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/why-europe-can-t-give-up-russian-gas-despite-sanctions-over-ukraine</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 16:18:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加密货币和利率将在 2025 年推动美国可转换债券增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/crypto-and-rates-to-drive-us-convertible-debt-growth-in-2025</link>
      <description><![CDATA[银行家们表示，美国可转换证券市场可能会在 2025 年测试其大流行时期的高点，利率仍将高于华尔街许多人的预期，而且加密资产相关策略没有很快消失的迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/crypto-and-rates-to-drive-us-convertible-debt-growth-in-2025</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 16:04:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国政治混乱致经济陷入低增长泥潭</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/france-s-political-chaos-traps-economy-in-low-growth-rut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国的政治和财政僵局导致经济陷入低增长，这给新任总理弗朗索瓦·贝鲁（Francois Bayrou）带来了挑选政府和迅速制定2025年预算的压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/france-s-political-chaos-traps-economy-in-low-growth-rut</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 16:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴西一天内通过两次美元拍卖来对抗实体经济的抛售</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/brazil-central-bank-steps-in-currency-markets-again-amid-selloff</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于人们对巴西债务和赤字膨胀的担忧日益加深，导致雷亚尔跌至历史最低水平，巴西周二采取了非常措施来阻止其货币急剧下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/brazil-central-bank-steps-in-currency-markets-again-amid-selloff</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 12:45:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国债券市场因英国央行降息押注减少而遭受重创</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/traders-see-fewer-boe-interest-rate-cuts-after-jump-in-uk-wages</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国政府借贷成本相对于德国升至几十年来的最高水平，因为交易员们对英国央行明年还能实施多少宽松政策越来越怀疑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/traders-see-fewer-boe-interest-rate-cuts-after-jump-in-uk-wages</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 07:56:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国银行完成厄瓜多尔 10 亿美元债务互换</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/bank-of-america-wraps-up-1-billion-debt-swap-for-ecuador</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国银行公司已完成一项 10 亿美元的交易，为厄瓜多尔部分债务进行再融资，并帮助资助保护亚马逊地区的森林、河流、湖泊和湿地。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/bank-of-america-wraps-up-1-billion-debt-swap-for-ecuador</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 07:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场综述：美国股市因数据和美联储关注而缩减跌幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员权衡强劲的美国零售销售数据并等待美联储的利率决定及其预测，股市缩减了早前的跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Dec 2024 22:35:43 GMT</pubDate>
